name: VIP SOUL
overview:
Vip Soul is an online social shopping club that give access to its members to branded and lifestyle goods up to 70% off the retail price. In this shopping club you can interact among the members and discover the best deals and promotions of your favorite fashion and lifestyle brands.

The customer has an A1 service cliente, he or she can pay not only with credit card , but also with cash or bank agent. It supported by chat, email. It s possible to track your order and also will be posible to discover the best style advices.
